{"tid":12853,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"男子遇火警不願意逃生 就是要看A片","createTime":"2016-11-29T23:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T10:13:50.000Z","uid":12709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77dc2c8375154c4e63d658952e2042de7fb18a01","tid":12853,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:15:30.000Z","msg":"德國漢堡一名男子為了要把A片看完，遇到了火警也不願意逃生，之後消防人員把他硬拖出來，才救了他一命。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，該名男子近日光顧漢堡著名的紅燈區「繩索街」(Reeperbahn)一間性商店，當時他租了一間包廂觀看A片，但店舖所處的大廈突然起火。隨後消防人員趕到，這時大廈已經濃煙密布，但男子堅持不要逃生，消防員只好破門把他拖出來。<br />\n<br />\n當他被救出後，竟然大喊：「我付了7.5歐元(約新台幣300元)，我還沒看完啦！」消防人員指，他被救出時處於「性興奮狀態」，之後他因為吸入濃煙不適要送醫。事件中另有2名店舖工作人員受傷。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"23123c69ee8645e40212a44e35fb187950905883","tid":12853,"uid":42372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:29:47.000Z","msg":"死都要睇A片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2d4a161f265f696d7b0692de7dbc836f4d9af9","tid":12853,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死都要睇A片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28fd77076c9a0e7743a63e9556245e676a0fa65","tid":12853,"uid":31903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死都要睇A片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死都要打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47ed2e4759b4dfbe79ba9fdf9e7074bccf9177b","tid":12853,"uid":30171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote